 <h2>
  <span id="Why_containers?">
  </span>
  <span class="mw-headline" id="Why_containers.3F">
   Why containers?
  </span>
  <span class="mw-editsection">
   <span class="mw-editsection-bracket">
    [
   </span>
   <a class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" href="/mediawiki/index.php?title=ITOM_Container_Deployment_Foundation:2019.05/WhitepaperContainerStandardsPolicy&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=T-1" title="Edit section: ">
    edit
   </a>
   <span class="mw-editsection-divider">
    |
   </span>
   <a href="/mediawiki/index.php?title=ITOM_Container_Deployment_Foundation:2019.05/WhitepaperContainerStandardsPolicy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=T-1" title="Edit section: ">
    edit source
   </a>
   <span class="mw-editsection-bracket">
    ]
   </span>
  </span>
 </h2>
 <p>
  <a class="image" onclick="javascript:loadingImage(this);">
   <img alt="cdferwp201801 image3.png" data-file-height="722" data-file-width="1764" height="368" src="/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/36/cdferwp201801_image3.png/900px-cdferwp201801_image3.png" srcset="/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/36/cdferwp201801_image3.png/1350px-cdferwp201801_image3.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/36/cdferwp201801_image3.png 2x" width="900"/>
  </a>
 </p>
 <p>
  The application landscape is changing, let’s list 4 main areas:
 </p>
 <ul>
  <li>
   Architecture: “glued” applications to loosely coupled services
  </li>
  <li>
   Process: slow changes to continuous updates
  </li>
  <li>
   Technology: human to machine operated
  </li>
  <li>
   Sourcing: single delivery to a hybrid delivery model
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p>
  The adoption of containers is driven by the transformation of applications, desire for higher productivity and agility and a SaaS like experience requirement.
 </p>
 <p>
  Write once run anywhere is an enticing proposition for any software developer and opens up new ways of delivering software with SaaS-like experience.
 </p>
 <h2>
  <span id="What_drives_container_adoption?">
  </span>
  <span class="mw-headline" id="What_drives_container_adoption.3F">
   What drives container adoption?
  </span>
  <span class="mw-editsection">
   <span class="mw-editsection-bracket">
    [
   </span>
   <a class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" href="/mediawiki/index.php?title=ITOM_Container_Deployment_Foundation:2019.05/WhitepaperContainerStandardsPolicy&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=T-2" title="Edit section: ">
